{"title_page": "2015 Nadeshiko League", "text_new": "{{Infobox football league season\n| competition      = [[L. League|Nadeshiko League]]\n| season           = 2015\n| winners          = [[NTV Beleza]]<br />13th Nadeshiko League title\n| relegated        = [[AS Elfen Saitama]]\n| league topscorer = [[Yuika Sugasawa]] (15 goals)\n| prevseason = [[2014 Nadeshiko League|2014]]\n| nextseason = [[2016 Nadeshiko League|2016]]\n}}\nThe 2015 [[L. League|Nadeshiko League]] season was won by [[NTV Beleza]], who have won the title 13 times.<ref name=nadeshiko_2015_results>{{cite web|title=2015 Schedule and Results|url=http://www.nadeshikoleague.jp/2015/exciting1/match/|publisher=Nadeshiko League|accessdate=28 November 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122163917/http://www.nadeshikoleague.jp/2015/exciting1/match/|archive-date=22 November 2015|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=2015 Nadeshiko League|url=http://www.futbol24.com/national/Japan/Women-Nadeshiko-League/2015/|publisher=Futbol 24|accessdate=29 November 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Nadeshiko League Division 1==\n\n===First stage : Regular series===\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|sortable_table=y\n|res_col_header=2nd Stage : Ex.Pts\n|team1=BEL|name_BEL=[[NTV Beleza]]\n|team2=LEO|name_LEO=[[INAC Kobe Leonessa]]\n|team3=SEN|name_SEN=[[Vegalta Sendai Ladies]]\n|team4=JEF|name_JEF=[[JEF United Ichihara Chiba Ladies]]\n|team5=ALB|name_ALB=[[Albirex Niigata Ladies]]\n|team6=RED|name_RED=[[Urawa Red Diamonds Ladies]]\n|team7=OYB|name_OYB=[[Okayama Yunogo Belle]]\n|team8=KUN|name_KUN=[[Iga Football Club Kunoichi|Iga F.C. Kunoichi]]\n|team9=SPE|name_SPE=[[Speranza F.C. Osaka-Takatsuki]]\n|team10=SAI|name_SAI=[[AS Elfen Saitama]]\n|win_BEL=13|draw_BEL=4|loss_BEL=1|gf_BEL=41|ga_BEL=9\n|win_LEO=13|draw_LEO=3|loss_LEO=2|gf_LEO=36|ga_LEO=18\n|win_SEN=11|draw_SEN=3|loss_SEN=4|gf_SEN=40|ga_SEN=26\n|win_JEF=8|draw_JEF=8|loss_JEF=2|gf_JEF=25|ga_JEF=12\n|win_ALB=8|draw_ALB=2|loss_ALB=8|gf_ALB=20|ga_ALB=