ate=28 November 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122163917/http://www.nadeshikoleague.jp/2015/exciting1/match/|archive-date=22 November 2015|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=2015 Nadeshiko League|url=http://www.futbol24.com/national/Japan/Women-Nadeshiko-League/2015/|publisher=Futbol 24|accessdate=29 November 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Nadeshiko League Division 1==\n\n===First stage : Regular series===\n{{fb cl header|sort=y|noqr=y}}\n|2nd Stage : Ex.Pts\n|- style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"\n|1||align=\"left\"|[[NTV Beleza]]||18||13||4||1||41||9|| 32||'''43'''||Championship League : 6\n|- style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"\n|2||align=\"left\"|[[INAC Kobe Leonessa]]||18||13||3||2||36||18|| 18||'''42'''||Championship League : 5\n|- style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"\n|3||align=\"left\"|[[Vegalta Sendai Ladies]]||18||11||3||4||40||26|| 14||'''36'''||Championship League : 4\n|- style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"\n|4||align=\"left\"|[[JEF United Ichihara Chiba Ladies]]||18||8||8||2||25||12|| 13||'''32'''||Championship League : 3\n|- style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"\n|5||align=\"left\"|[[Albirex Niigata Ladies]]||18||8||2||8||20||17|| 3||'''26'''||Championship League : 2\n|- style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"\n|6||align=\"left\"|[[Urawa Red Diamonds Ladies]]||18||6||5||7||20||18|| 2||'''23'''||Championship League : 1\n|- style=\"background:#FFCCCC;\"\n|7||align=\"left\"|[[Okayama Yunogo Belle]]||18||5||3||10||16||34|| -18||'''18'''||Position Playoff : 6\n|- style=\"background:#ffcccc\"\n|8||align=\"left\"|[[Iga Football Club Kunoichi|Iga F.C. Kunoichi]]||18||4||2||12||12||30|| -18||'''14'''||Position Playoff : 5\n|- style=\"background:#ffcccc\"\n|9||align=\"left\"|[[Speranza F.C. Osaka-Takatsuki]]||18||2||4||12||14||32|| -18||'''10'''||Position Playoff : 3\n|- style=\"background:#ffcccc\"\n|10||align=\"left\"|[[AS Elfen Saitama]]||18||2||2||14||8||36|| -28||'''8'''||Position Playoff : 3\n|}\n\n===Second stage : Exciting series===\n\n====Championship league====\n{{fb 